## Laundry Service Landing Page

A responsive laundry service landing page built using HTML and CSS.
This project is designed to provide a clean and modern user interface for a laundry business website.

## Features
Responsive design for mobile and desktop
Modern hero section layout
Clean typography and spacing
Call-to-action button
Image and content alignment using Flexbox
Mobile-first responsive media queries
Technologies Used
HTML5
CSS3
Flexbox
Media Queries
Project Structure
project-folder/
│
├── index.html
├── style.css
└── image.png
Responsive Design

## The website is fully responsive and adapts to different screen sizes:

Desktop View
Tablet View
Mobile View
How to Run the Project
Download or clone the repository
Open the project folder
Run index.html in your browser
